name: MusicEventType
desc: MIDI and other music event types, used by music event iterator functions.

items.name: var kMusicEventType_ExtendedNote: UInt32
items.desc: A non-MIDI music event with variable number of parameters.

items.name: var kMusicEventType_ExtendedTempo: UInt32
items.desc: An event that signals a change in tempo, in beats-per-minute.

items.name: var kMusicEventType_MIDINoteMessage: UInt32
items.desc: A MIDI note-on message, including duration.

items.name: var kMusicEventType_MIDIChannelMessage: UInt32
items.desc: A MIDI channel message, other than note control.

items.name: var kMusicEventType_AUPreset: UInt32
items.desc: An event containing an audio unit user preset dictionary.
